title: 739. Reaction to Cam Newton Signing with Panthers & DJ's Top 25 Rookies at Midseason
itunes:title: 739. Reaction to Cam Newton Signing with Panthers & DJ's Top 25 Rookies at Midseason
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys react to the Panthers signing quarterback Cam Newton. Next, the pair discuss which is the better head coaching job, the Carolina Panthers or LSU. After that, DJ goes through his top 25 rookies at midseason. To wrap up the show, the duo preview the Thursday Night Football game between the Baltimore Ravens and Miami Dolphins.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
